name: Historic Gallente SKINs Crate
description:
This crate grants one random Gallente ship SKIN from the following SKIN lines: Ace of Podhunters, Caille Neon, Green Demons, Heartsurge, Inner Zone Shipping, Inner Zone Vanguard, Kopis Edge, Ruby Sungrazer, Valimor Legacy, and Yoiul Festival YC121.

With 28 SKINs available, each crate has a 3.57% chance to contain a specific SKIN.
